  <h2 id="when-to-use-this-component">When to use a fieldset</h2>
  <p>Use a fieldset when you need to show a relationship between multiple form inputs. For example, to group a set of text inputs into a single fieldset when asking for an address or <a href="/design-system/components/date-input">a date</a>.</p>

  {{ designExample({
