    type: "as-heading"
  }) }}

  <h2>Accessibility</h2>
  <p>On question pages containing a set of inputs, group them using a <code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> and include the question as the <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code>. This helps screen reader users understand that the inputs are all related to that question.</p>
  <p>Include any important general help text in the legend if it would help the user fill in the form, and you cannot write it as <a href="/design-system/components/text-input#using-hint-text">hint text</a>. Keep it as short as possible because screen readers may repeat the legend for each input in the fieldset.</p>

